&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;img src=&amp;quot;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9pbWdtZC5vc3MtY24tc2hhbmdoYWkuYWxpeXVuY3MuY29tL0JFUlRfSU1HLyVFNCVCRCU4RCVFNyVCRCVBRSVFNSVCNSU4QyVFNSU4NSVBNSVFOCVBNyVBMyVFOSU4NyU4QS5wbmc=&#34;&gt;https://imgmd.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/BERT_IMG/ 位置嵌入解释.png&lt;/span&gt;&amp;quot; alt=&amp;quot;img&amp;quot; style=&amp;quot;zoom:50%;&amp;quot; /&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;
